// Demo for the taclet-generating transformer spike (branch bubel/lemma-taclet-spike).
//
// Right-click exactly on a "5 + 7" subterm and apply "introduce_addLitLemma":
// a new node appears, the sequent is unchanged, but the goal-local taclet
// addLitLemma_5_7 { \find(5 + 7) \replacewith(12) } is now available.
// Right-click "5 + 7" again to apply it like any ordinary taclet.
//
// The same single introduction serves all three occurrences (and, after andRight,
// all branches below the introduction node). Introducing again after pruning or
// on a parallel branch reuses the identical taclet - no duplicate is created.

\problem {
    5 + 7 = 12
  & 2 * (5 + 7) = 24
  & (5 + 7) + 1 = 13
}
